<p>Since this concert, Maria has put together <a href="http://www.mariafinkelmeier.com/news/2014/9/26/frostbeat-20">ANOTHER Frost Beat night</a> with Amy Garapic. Hopefully I’ll get to come back sometime and make some more ice music!</p>
